main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 2456/93 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in paragraph 5 of Annex V '24 hours' is replaced by '48 hours';
2. in the first subparagraph of paragraph 2.1.3 of Annex VII, the last sentence is replaced by the following: 'Fat underlying the deckle and the sternum must be removed.'
